messages.text: That will be made known soon.
You put up a fight… I was surprised…
It’ll all come back to you soon.
Like I said, you will know later.
But for now, I want you to solve a riddle…
Don’t do that. You’ll mess up the floor.
y am I chained 2 the floor?!?!?
I just want to play some games.
You may have a chance at freedom.
If you can solve my riddle.
It’s quite simple and you’re a smart girl, so I have faith.
It will only message me silly girl.
Solve a riddle and I might tell you :)
how did i get here?!? y am I here?!?!
What bears the truth and lies…
What is not judged by its size??
im not playin ur messed up games!!
tell me wat ive done wrong!!!
I never said you did anything wrong…?
then wat am I doin here?!?
Do you really want to die?
if u don’t get me out of here!!
Ah, it’s rather what you haven’t done.
You’ve always ignored me… Never acknowledged me…
watever I have done, im sorry!!!
Solve the riddle and you may survive…
Or be crushed. Up to you.
do u not care wat happens to me?!?!?
If you solve the riddle, stopping the walls, I’ll have you in one piece…
But if you’re crushed, I can just drink your pretty little blood :)
That hurts Jamie… That really does.
You have control over that. Solve the riddle.
holds truth and lies and not judged by size..
I wish I could. But this is for you to figure out.
Remember when I asked you to help in my garden…
idk wat the hell ur talking about!!
Or remember the time I asked for you to watch Pablo.
See, this hurts me… You don’t remember the name of my dog…
I never ever meant much to you.
jus tell me WHO U R?!?!
I’ve lived next to you all your life… Not once did you say hi…
You were always a pretty girl..
I’ve enjoyed watching the women you have become.
Shame you’ll have to be crushed.
the answer to the riddle is ‘words’!
Congrats, you saved yourself with minutes to spare.
Not in that way. I promised you might escape.
You’re gonna enjoy our life together :)
